      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392664&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7442&rangeEnd=7497",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8e5329307192b8588e5c086?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=7442&rangeEnd=7497"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26392664_5_2019-2083",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2019-2083",
      "markText": "如果你认为消息很可能刺激大市看好或看淡，便不要在市场走势与你的看法一致之前，凭个人的判断入市，因为市场反应并不一定如你所预见的。",
      "totalCount": 306,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392664&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2019&rangeEnd=2083",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8e5329307192b8588e5c086?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2019&rangeEnd=2083"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26392664_5_2973-3011",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2973-3011",
      "markText": "我赚钱并非因为我投机买卖，而是因为支持股票的走势非常强劲，我只是随大流而已。",
      "totalCount": 253,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392664&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2973&rangeEnd=3011",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8e5329307192b8588e5c086?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2973&rangeEnd=3011"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26392664_5_372-428",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "372-428",
      "markText": "投机始终是世上最引人入胜的游戏，可是不适合愚昧、懒惰、性急的人士，也不适宜只懂赚快钱的冒险家，否则只会晚景凄凉。",
      "totalCount": 208,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392664&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=372&rangeEnd=428",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8e5329307192b8588e5c086?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=372&rangeEnd=428"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26392664_4_402-465",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "402-465",
      "markText": "投资是一个玻璃瓶，外面看简单透明，似乎谁都能一眼看穿。但投资又是个万花筒，因为等你真正上手仔细看，里面的玄妙又会让人晕头转向。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392664&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=402&rangeEnd=465",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8e5329307192b8588e5c086?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=402&rangeEnd=465"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26392664_5_3586-3610",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3586-3610",
      "markText": "只要股价升势持续，市场走势正确，便毋须急于套现。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392664&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3586&rangeEnd=3610",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8e5329307192b8588e5c086?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3586&rangeEnd=3610"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26392664_11_1901-1975",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1901-1975",
      "markText": "还有一个要点值得记住：投机者应该定下规矩，在每次赚钱后把一半的盈利锁在保险箱内，并持之以恒。投机者从华尔街拿到的唯一款项，就是赚钱后从账户提走的钱。",
      "totalCount": 136,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392664&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1901&rangeEnd=1975",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8e5329307192b8588e5c086?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1901&rangeEnd=1975"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26392664_5_2574-2625",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2574-2625",
      "markText": "我要说的是，当对某只股票有具体看法后，不要急于行动，而是细心观察该股票或市场，按照基本的准则伺机而动。",
      "totalCount": 132,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392664&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2574&rangeEnd=2625",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8e5329307192b8588e5c086?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2574&rangeEnd=2625"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26392664_5_4002-4056",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4002-4056",
      "markText": "投资获利时大可不必理会，不过出现损失时便要小心防范。投机者需有两手准备，吃小亏时可先行平仓，以防日后吃大亏。",
      "totalCount": 128,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392664&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4002&rangeEnd=4056",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8e5329307192b8588e5c086?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4002&rangeEnd=4056"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26392664_6_1354-1440",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1354-1440",
      "markText": "所以说，不管你是股神还是普通交易者，当市场先生为你指明方向的时候，一定不可忽视，更要不得的就是屁股决定脑袋，因为满仓而看多，因为空仓而看空，那是新入行的投资者最常犯的错误。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392664&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1354&rangeEnd=1440",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8e5329307192b8588e5c086?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1354&rangeEnd=1440"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26392664_11_1092-1188",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1092-1188",
      "markText": "我只知道经纪能提供的唯一可靠消息，就是补仓通知。当你收到补仓通知时，便要平仓。你错估市场形势了，为何还要连老本都赔上呢？保留资金，静待时机，把钱押注在更有吸引力的股票上，总比明显赔钱的交易好。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392664&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1092&rangeEnd=1188",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8e5329307192b8588e5c086?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1092&rangeEnd=1188"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26392664_15_539-603",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "539-603",
      "markText": "假设你计划买入某只股票500股，便要首先买入100股，如果大市上升，便再买入100股，依此类推。每次的买入价都比前一次的高一点。",
      "totalCount": 126,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26392664&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=539&rangeEnd=603",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/8e5329307192b8588e5c086?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=539&rangeEnd=603"
    },
